description: Normalized log2ratio protein abundance estimates for the CPTAC2 Prospective Ovarian PNNL Proteome Qeplus study (PDC Study ID: PDC000118) were obtained via the PDC API quantDataMatrix endpoint. These data are part of the CPTAC2 Confirmatory project. More information on the pipeline and the results generated by it can be found here: https://pdc.cancer.gov/data-dictionary/harmonization.html
friendlyName: CPTAC2 CONFIRMATORY OVARIAN PNNL PROTEOME QEPLUS
